	Allow for extensions other than .a for preloaded modules.
	* libltdl/m4/ltdl.m4 (_LTDL_SETUP): Define LT_LIBEXT.
	* libltdl/ltdl.c (lt_dladvise_preload): Use it.
	Reported by Ralf Wildenhues.

