	* libltdl/m4/libtool.m4 (_LT_DECL_OBJDUMP): new macro ensures
	that $OBJDUMP is always defined sanely.
	(_LT_SYS_DYNAMIC_LINKER): call it.
	(_LT_CHECK_MAGIC_METHOD): call it.

