2008-02-01  Gary V. Vaughan  <gary@gnu.org>

	* tests/cdemo, tests/depdemo, tests/fcdemo, tests/pdemo,
	tests/demo, tests/f77demo, tests/mdemo, tests/tagdemo
	(distclean-local): Remove compiler file droppings left by
